  "instructions": [
    "Heat the donabe over medium heat and render 2 tbsp pork fat until liquid.",
    "Add diced onions and minced garlic, sauté until softened and fragrant.",
    "Stir in cubed pork shoulder and brown on all sides.",
    "Mix in tamarind paste, makham cheese cubes, and ground cumin, cooking for 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in coconut milk, vegetable stock, and soy sauce, then stir to combine.",
    "Sprinkle smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper, then bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and let the stew cook for 45 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro before serving hot."
  ],
